    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="generate_ts_8py_source" kindref="compound">generateTs.py</ref></computeroutput> parses <computeroutput>instruments.xml</computeroutput> and create a fake <computeroutput><ref refid="instrumentsxml_8h_source" kindref="compound">instrumentsxml.h</ref></computeroutput> file</para></listitem><listitem><para>gen-instruments-projectfile creates a pro file for the translations, so we can run lupdate and lrelease on it</para></listitem><listitem><para>the TS file is loaded by MuseScore and the instruments are translated when the instruments.xml file is loaded</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><heading level="2">If instruments.xml is modified </heading>
</para><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>run <computeroutput><ref refid="generate_ts_8py_source" kindref="compound">generateTs.py</ref></computeroutput> and lupdate.sh</para></listitem><listitem><para>push the new file updated ts en_US file to transifex </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
